        <Parent_String>Ostreoida (order) [300310173], Pteriomorphia (subclass) [300310172], Bivalvia (class) [300259074], Mollusca (phylum) [300266510], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
